<h1>About Melodic PHP</h1>
<p>A modern PHP 8.2+ framework built with clarity and performance in mind.</p>

<h2>Core Principles</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Controller &rarr; Service &rarr; Query/Command</strong> &mdash; clean layered architecture</li>
    <li><strong>CQRS</strong> &mdash; explicit read/write separation at the data access layer</li>
    <li><strong>Dependency injection</strong> &mdash; constructor auto-wiring with no magic</li>
    <li><strong>JWT-based security</strong> &mdash; multi-provider auth with claims-based authorization</li>
    <li><strong>No facades, no mediator</strong> &mdash; direct, explicit code flow you can follow</li>
</ul>

<h2>Requirements</h2>
<ul>
    <li>PHP 8.2+</li>
    <li>PDO extension</li>
    <li><code>firebase/php-jwt</code> for token handling</li>
</ul>

